These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, disco, r&b, punk
There 4 different types of food: peas, tomato, pear, corn
1. the person eating corn is not to the right of the person eating peas##8
2. the person eating corn is on the right of the fan rock##1
3. the fan disco is on the left or right of the fan r&b##3
4. the fan punk is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
5. the fan punk is not to the left of the person eating corn##8
6. the person eating pear is somewhere to the left of the fan disco##5
7. the fan disco is somewhere between the fan rock and the person eating tomato##7
8. the fan disco and the person eating corn have the same parity positions##9
9. the fan r&b and the person eating peas have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | rock | disco | r&b     | punk |
| Pet           | pear   | corn     | tomato | peas  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, firefighter, pilot, accountant
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, may, april, december
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december and the firefighter have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
4. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the accountant##8
5. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
6. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
7. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
8. the accountant is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | accountant     | pilot    | scientist | firefighter    |
| Hobby      | september | may | april      | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, ritmeester, dunhill, game
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, ivory, black, aquamarine
1. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
2. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
6. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
7. the person who likes grey is not to the left of the person who likes ivory##8
8. the ritmeester-smoker and the person who likes ivory have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | ritmeester    | dunhill   | prince    | game  |
| Food       | ivory | aquamarine | grey | black |

