.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, italian, mexican, british
City: hamburg, marseilles, london, berlin
1. the person traveling to hamburg is the italian##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the mexican##3
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the egyptian##1
6. the british and the person traveling to berlin have the same parity positions##9
7. the mexican is on the left or right of the egyptian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | british | mexican | egyptian  | italian |
| Music-Genre   | london             | marseilles          | berlin | hamburg    |

