.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, april, february, june
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, chaman, cain, montecristo
1. the person who's birthday is in february is not the cain-smoker##6
2. the swisher-smoker and the person who's birthday is in september have different parity positions##9
3. the chaman-smoker and the person who's birthday is in april have different parity positions##9
4. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
5. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is not the chaman-smoker##6
7. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
8. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
9. the montecristo-smoker is not the person who's birthday is in june##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | september | february | june  | april |
| Pet           | chaman   | swisher     | cain | montecristo      |

