.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, amber, apricot, grey
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, scooter, van, taxi
1. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
3. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5
4. the person driving the bus and the person who likes apricot have the same parity positions##9
5. the person who likes grey and the person driving the bus have different parity positions##9
6. the person driving the van is not to the left of the person who likes red##8
7. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
8. the person who likes amber is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | amber | red | apricot | grey |
| Nationality   | taxi        | van    | bus   | scooter |

