3. the swisher-smoker is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |  2   |     3     |      4       |
