3. the person who likes turquise and the person eating grapefruit have different parity positions##9
4. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person eating tomato##8
6. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
