The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, february, july
1. the security-guard is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in november##7
2. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the dressmaker is on the left of the scientist##1
5. the scientist is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
6. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
7. the dressmaker and the person who's birthday is in july have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | dressmaker | scientist | security-guard | nurse |
| Pet     | november     | february     | july     | june    |

