There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, white, purple, turquise
1. the person who likes turquise is not to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who likes turquise have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
5. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the person who likes white and the person who likes turquise##7
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | singing | rock-climbing   | writing | magic-tricks |
| Transport   | purple   | white | ebony    | turquise      |

