2. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the fan rock is not to the left of the fan pop##8
4. the fan pop is on the left or right of the fan techno##3
5. the fan pop is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the fan rock##1
8. the fan disco is the owner of the turtle##1
9. the fan pop and the owner of the ferret have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | techno   | pop    | rock | disco    |
| Nationality   | hedgehog | ferret | pony   | turtle |

