.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-15::.
4 different games are played: chess, poker, whist, mah-jongg
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, sports, fantasy, adventure
1. the person playing poker and the person watching adventure movies have the same parity positions##9
2. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
3. the person playing chess is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the person watching adventure movies##7
4. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the person playing chess##7
5. the person watching sports movies is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
7. the person playing whist is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | mah-jongg | chess | poker | whist  |
| Music-Genre   | horror    | sports | adventure | fantasy |

