.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
House: townhouse, wooden, farmhouse, victorian
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, software-developer, mechanic, engineer
 1. the wooden house and the mechanic have the same parity positions##9
 2. the farmhouse house is not to the right of the wooden house##8
 3. the police-officer is somewhere between the wooden house and the townhouse house##7
 4. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
 5. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
 6. the mechanic is not to the left of the victorian house##8
 7. the victorian house and the software-developer have the same parity positions##9
 8. the victorian house is on the left or right of the engineer##3
 9. the engineer is in an odd position##4
10. the victorian house is not to the right of the police-officer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | townhouse  | victorian | farmhouse  | wooden |
| Music-Genre   | engineer | mechanic     | police-officer | software-developer     |

