.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, entrepreneur, accountant, freelancer
4 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, canasta, backgammon
 1. the freelancer is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
 4. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
 5. the person playing billiard is not the entrepreneur##6
 6. the freelancer is not to the right of the journalist##8
 7. the freelancer and the person playing scrabble have the same parity positions##9
 8. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the accountant##8
 9. the freelancer is the person playing scrabble##1
10. the entrepreneur and the person playing scrabble have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | entrepreneur    | accountant        | freelancer   | journalist      |
| Hobby      | backgammon | canasta | scrabble | billiard |

 